(131, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Bhutan  tour packages', 'Bhutan_555x555.jpg', 'bhutan.jpg', '7', 'The very words give us glimpses of a remote land replete with monks, monasteries, yaks, Buddhist art and much more. Bhutan is no longer so remote and features as a must-see destination.            ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bhutan Tour Packages</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tucked in the lap of the Himalayas, Bhutan is one of the last remaining Kingdoms. The Shangri-La is set amid the world&rsquo;s most beautiful mountain range. It is blessed with ethereal views, vibrant culture, trekking opportunities and what can only be described as the best time of your life. With Bhutan tour packages, discover the bliss of the last paradise on Earth. Home to snow-draped peaks, lush valleys, ancient monasteries, incredible architecture, colorful culture, happy people and experiences that bring a smile to your face.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When the measure is happiness, Bhutan is among the happiest places in the world. This fact reveals how prosperous the country is and how well they treat their guests. Every moment of a Bhutan holiday is made special as is every experience worth cherishing. If its mystery you seek, then the country is shrouded in many fables of the old. If you would love to escape the crowds then there are so many of the unexplored pristine spots that you would definitely lose count. And what can one say about the plethora of places to visit and things to do, each one is an important aspect of Bhutan tour.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The Buddhist nation is known for the colorful prayer flags fluttering in the air, prayer wheels and scenic monasteries. The grand examples of traditional design and architecture, they have much to offer to enthrall visitors. The iconic Tiger&rsquo;s Nest is an out-of-the world lying precariously over sheer cliff tops. Many of the known and the explored monasteries stand as majestic guards over pictorial towns. Buddhist culture is also unmissable part of Bhutan packages. Their traditions add to the beautiful experiences the country has to offer. Masked dances, songs, dances, plays, dramatization, and other stage efficiencies make the culture endearing.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Choose Bhutan travel packages that cover major tourist attractions like Tiger&rsquo;s Nest Monastery, Punakha Dzong, or Pungtang Dechen Phodrang (Palace of Great Happiness), Taktsang Monastery, Phobjikha and Gangtey Valley, National Folk Heritage Museum, Trashi Chhoe Dzong, etc. Excursion to National Memorial Stupa, Textile Museum, the Changangkha Temple, etc. are also a must.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The heavenly food, mixture of Indian, Chinese, Tibetan delicacies is what makes Bhutan holidays all the more special. The charming hotels with the most lavish amenities only enhance the thrill. While with family you can creates the most beautiful memories, Bhutan honeymoon packages is an absolute stunner. What better than to begin a new life in the heavenly bliss.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Choose any of the Bhutan holiday packages and cherish memories of a lifetime. The traffic light free country does not know to stop the traffic of excitements. The mesmerizing country welcomes all kinds of travelers equally. Be it your get away from your schedules, family vacation, romantic honeymoon, adventure or juts finding your happiness, browse through our well-crafted Bhutan tours from India.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_3', 'Sinda_tours_travels_3'),
(132, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Azerbaijan tour packages', 'Azerbaijan_555x555.jpg', 'Azerbaijan Tour Packages.jpg', '7', 'Beautiful nature, characterized by a diverse landscape, magnificent architecture, rich cultural heritage as well as the overall development of the country present lots of opportunities for pastime.             ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Azerbaijan Tour Packages</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Showcasing a perfect confluence of the east and the west, Azerbaijan is replete with a number of attractions. It is because of these charms, that the Azerbaijan tour packages from India remain in huge demand. Often known as the &lsquo;Land of Fire&rsquo;, the country never fails to amuse the visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Be it the Fire Mountain, Mud Volcanoes, seaside resorts or ancient mosques, everything seems to cast a spell on the tourists. Home to astounding architectures, engaging cities, National Parks and majestic sea, Azerbaijan is nothing less than a dreamland.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Plan a trip to Azerbaijan and escape into mountain or beaches, the country has something to offer to everybody. Flaunting two UNESCO World Heritage Sites, the intriguing destination enjoys a rich history. Azerbaijan is an ideal place to cherish several experiences under a single roof.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_2', 'Sinda_tours_travels_2'),
(133, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Cambodia tour packages', 'Cambodia_555x555.jpg', 'Cambodia tour packages.jpg', '7', 'Cambodia is famous for a Hindu temple known as Angkor Wat temple. Here the sunrise is the most captivate thing.                         ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Cambodia Tour Packages</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Cambodia is one of the most fascinating Southeast Asian destinations, which can best be explored by opting for Cambodia tour packages, designed by us in a meticulous manner. The place has gems like rich history and culture, busy cities, traditional villages, thick jungles and ancient Khmer temples. During your Cambodia tours, do not miss visiting Angor Wat, the biggest Hindu temple complex. The site of River Mekong flowing towards Tonle Sap Lake is a memorable one and must be visited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Cambodia holiday packages are incomplete without a visit to the pristine Sihanoukville beach. Other attractions include capital city Phnom Penh, Kirirom, Rattanakiri, and Kampot. Baypn and the ruins of Khmer empire are unmissable too.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_4', 'Sinda_tours_travels_4'),
(134, '2019-12-23', 'International', 'Nepal  tour packages', 'nepal.jpg', 'nepal.jpg', '7', 'According to , major tourist activities include wilderness and adventure activities such as mountain biking, bungee jumping, rock climbing, and mountain climbing ,etc.                                                                        ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>Best Nepal Tour Packages</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Nestled amidst the mighty Himalayas, Nepal is known for its rich culture, traditions and some of the highest mountain peaks in the world that includes Mt. Everest. If in any case, you are thinking of bowled over by the stunning snow-laden mountains, then you must visit Nepal right now. From monasteries, temples, wildlife, stupas, enchanting places to anything and everything that you can imagine, the country has it all.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">With our collection of the best Nepal tour packages, you can go to the amazing tourist spots in the country to get the feel of scenic beauty, local culture, traditions and idyllic atmosphere to the fullest. Getting deep insights into the exquisite culture of the place is an eye-opening experience and can be better cherished with a well-planned tour package like the ones offered by us.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">The rugged terrain of Nepal has also paved path for various types of adventure tours. One can embark on a number of adventure trips such as mountain hiking, Nepal trekking, mountain cycling, mountain biking and other sports to give you that much-cherished adrenaline rush. You can go for adventure tours to places such as Annapurna base camp, Everest base camp and so on.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Our collection of Nepal travel packages from Delhi as well as Kathmandu and elsewhere will take you to some of the most sacred temples, mighty Himalayan peaks and UNESCO inscribed World Heritage Sites. With us by your side, you can rest assured that your Nepal Trip will be the one you will love to cherish forever.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Take a break from the hectic schedule and plan your Nepal Bhutan tour right now! This tour is designed based on your tastes and preferences. Offering much more than just normal sightseeing, the tour allows you delight in some memorable experiences.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">The Nepal Bhutan Tibet tour further allows you to get a glimpse into the rich culture and heritage. No doubt, Nepal as well as the Himalayan region in Bhutan, Tibet and North East India present a sight to behold. Besides, the tour also gives you a chance to treat your taste buds to some sizzling momos and other Tibetan delicacies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_6', 'Sinda_tours_travels_6'),
(140, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Madhya Pradesh Tours Packages', 'Madhya_Pradesh__555x555.jpg', 'Madhya Pradesh.jpg', '7', 'Popularly known as the heart of India, Madhya Pradesh is famous for its natural beauty and cultural heritage. The rich and exotic flora & fauna, historical monuments, fort & palaces.... ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\">Madhya Pradesh Tour Packages</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Popularly known as the heart of India, Madhya Pradesh is famous for its natural beauty and cultural heritage. The rich and exotic flora &amp; fauna, historical monuments, fort &amp; palaces, high mountain ranges, thick green forests, and diverse culture of Madhya Pradesh allure tourists from all over the world. Madhya Pradesh was ruled by a number of rulers from different dynasties. Because of the rule of different rulers, today, Madhya Pradesh offers every visitor with different tourist attractions which feature different forms of architectural styles.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Madhya Pradesh is most popularly known for housing the famous Kanha National Park and Bandhavgarh National Park which is known for its rich flora and fauna. Also, the state is famous for the Khajuraho Group of Monuments which has been declared as World Heritage Sites by UNESCO. Sanchi and Bhimbetka are other famous attractions of Madhya Pradesh which have been declared as World Heritage Sites by UNESCO. Other popular attractions of the state include Gwalior, Ujjain, Bhopal, Pachmarhi, Orchha and Jabalpur. The star attraction of Madhya Pradesh is the wide variety of cuisines it offers. Popular cuisines offered in the state include Rajasthani and Gujarati cuisines.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">There is a lot to explore in this incredible state of India. Pack up your bags and get ready to enjoy a holidays in Madhya Pradesh with Madhya Pradesh Tour Packages from Indian Holiday. There is a lot to explore in this incredible state of India. Pack up your bags and get ready to enjoy a unique traveling experience in the colorful state of Madhya Pradesh with Madhya Pradesh Tour Packages from Indian Holiday.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Madhya _Pradesh', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Madhya _Pradesh'),
(141, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Rajasthan Tour Packages', 'rajasthan_555x555.jpg', 'Rajasthan.jpg', '7', 'Given a chance to time travel and relish the magical expanse of Royal Rajasthan, you wouldn’t stop yourself from living each moment twice.....', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Rajasthan Tour Packages&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Given a chance to time travel and relish the magical expanse of Royal Rajasthan, you wouldn&rsquo;t stop yourself from living each moment twice. After all, it is not just a state, it is the pride of its bygone rulers and the joy in the voice of people who say &lsquo;Padharo Mhare Desh&rsquo;. The desire to catch the floating bubbles of culture, traditions, history and its royalty never ends, but travelers can at least start from somewhere with our Rajasthan tour Packages.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#4f81bd\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Why is Rajasthan famous for its tourism?</span></strong></strong></span></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">One destination, innumerable attractions! Tourists from all over the world find the royal state of Rajasthan a prime tourist destination in India. Owing to a number of vibrant cities Jodhpur and Jaipur, traditional puppet show, its folk dance &amp; music, palaces and forts, golden Desert, delectable food, colorful festivals, Shopping etc., Rajasthan cast a spell.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Traditional puppet show &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>Nowhere else you&rsquo;ll get to witness and listen to the stories of the Kings and Queens in such an entertaining way! Decorated puppets dancing to the traditional tunes and narrating amazing incidents present a sight to behold. Only Rajasthanis can keep alive the old-age tradition of puppet-show with such grace.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Folk Dance &amp; Music &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>It is the folk dance and music of the Rajasthan that urges you to tap your foot and match some steps with the locals. The magic of traditional instruments like pungi or been will make you leave all your worries behind.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Forts and palaces -</strong>&nbsp;The very name of Rajasthan conjures up the image of hilltop fortresses, maharajas with scimitars riding the painted elephants, the exquisitely carved havelis and the royal hunting grounds.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Golden Desert &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>The soft smooth silky golden sand covering a vast stretch tickles you when it slips under your feet. Appearing to be glittering liquid gold, the desert is the pride of Rajasthan and a perfect place to spend the night under the star-laden sky.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Delectable Food &ndash;</strong>&nbsp;Rajasthani cuisines are surely a treat to your taste buds and make this Rajawadi land of Rajputs a paradise for foodies.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In fact, we&#39;re here to Rajasthan travel guide, Our Rajasthan holiday packages are designed to offer you a peek into the era where all you get to relish are opulence and artistry. These small things counted together make Rajasthan one of the most popular tourist places in India.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Rajasthan', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Rajasthan'),
(142, '2019-09-06', 'India', 'Goa Tours packages', 'Goa_555x555.jpg', 'Goa.jpg', '7', 'Our fine collection of Goa tour packages help you cherish memorable holidays in Goa amidst the swaying palms, white sands & sparkling waters. Savor delicious cuisines, enjoy the vibrant nightlife....                        ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Goa Holiday Packages</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Our fine collection of Goa tour packages help you cherish memorable holidays in Goa amidst the swaying palms, white sands &amp; sparkling waters. Savor delicious cuisines, enjoy the vibrant nightlife and just let go of yourself with the characteristic susegad vibe. Practice yoga and meditation or rejuvenate yourself with therapeutic spa sessions at one of the fine luxury hotels in Goa. Our meticulously designed Goa holiday packages include all these and much more.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Goa also happens to be one of the most popular places to go for honeymoon in India. With this mind, we present the best <strong>Goa honeymoon tour packages</strong>. These packages help you curate memories of a lifetime by cherishing unmatched experiences. Stroll on the soft sand while holding each other&rsquo;s hand. Marvel at the spectacular sunset views and transform your evening into a magical affair.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">We not only cater to the needs of the newly wedded couples but also have a lot in store for avid travelers. Our <strong>Goa family tour packages</strong> allow you to experience the beauty of sparkling beaches and delight in a lush countryside ambiance. Reckoned as one of the finest beach destinations in India, the &lsquo;Party Capital&rsquo; lures holidaymakers from every nook and corner. The best time to visit Goa is from October till March. However, one should not miss planning <strong>North and South Goa tour</strong> in December and February to participate in various festivals.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Choose from any of the Goa travel package&nbsp;offered by IHPL and you will be transferred to the land of sand, sun and beaches. Boasting of a potpourri of colonial wonders, architecture, beaches, and the majestic forts, Goa promises to leave you spellbound. Trying your hands on the various adventure activities including water sports is one of the best things to do in Goa.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Goa&rsquo;s unique culture and lifestyle will urge you to plan a trip again and again. To help you with that, we have&nbsp;holiday trip to Goa. Crafted specially for you, these packages include everything that you are going to love about the lively state.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Goa', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Goa'),
(143, '2019-09-06', 'India', 'Agra Tours Package', 'Agra__555x555.jpg', 'Agra.jpg', '7', 'Agra has become almost synonymous with the legendary Taj Mahal. Several travel packages are offered to the tourists to make their vacation a delightful experience....            ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Holiday Packages in Agra&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Agra has become almost synonymous with the legendary Taj Mahal. Several travel packages are offered to the tourists to make their vacation a delightful experience.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">To make the tour a memorable one, choose form the various tour packages like honeymoon tour package, fort and palaces tour package, wildlife tours, golden triangle tours, heritage and cultural tours and city sightseeing tours.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Agra', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Agra'),
(144, '2019-09-06', 'India', 'Himachal Pradesh Tour package ', 'Himachal_Pradesh__555x555.jpg', 'Himachal Pradesh.jpg', '7', 'If your idea of holiday in India is being footloose with Himalayas and communion with nature, nothing beats Himachal Pradesh literally meaning “the land in the lap of Himalayas”. ...                                                ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Himachal Pradesh Tour Packages</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">If your idea of holiday in India is being footloose with Himalayas and communion with nature, nothing beats Himachal Pradesh literally meaning &ldquo;the land in the lap of Himalayas&rdquo;. With Himachal Tour Packages<strong>, </strong>explore picturesque hill stations, gushing waterfalls, abundant wildlife, emerald lakes, Trans Himalayan treks, snowcapped mountains and the barren beauty of upper Himalayas.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Our collection of Himachal Pradesh Holiday Packages is ideally suited for diverse themes when it comes to planning your holidays in India. Choose any of the Himachal tour packages for couple and cherish your honeymoon in India at Shimla, Dalhousie and Manali. Endowed with natural beauty, these popular hill stations are a must add-ons in any of the <strong>honeymoon packages</strong>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">For adventure tours in Himachal Pradesh, take your pick from best Himachal Tour Packages featuring destinations in Lahaul and Spiti Valley. There are several high altitude lakes, thrilling trekking routes and snowcapped mountain to be explored. You can also go paragliding in Bir Billing by choosing from our collection of<strong> </strong>Himachal Pradesh Tour Packages from Delhi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Not only from Delhi, but Himachal tour packages from Mumbai are also highly preferred because of the number of charms the state offers. Whether traveling solo, with family or with friends Himachal welcomes all kinds of travelers. This is also the reason that Himachal tour packages from Ahmedabad remain in huge demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Replete with temples, hill stations, lakes and snowcapped mountains, vacations in Himachal Pradesh are ideally suited for family summer holidays in India, honeymoon tour, <strong>adventure of trekking</strong>, road trips, motorcycle tours and heritage holiday.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Himachal', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Himachal'),
(147, '2019-12-23', 'India', 'Shimla and Manali Tour Package', 'simla.png', 'shimla.jpg', '6', 'Manali is a high-altitude Himalayan resort town in India’s northern Himachal Pradesh state.             ', '<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Day 1: Delhi - Shimla (380 kms)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nOn Arrival in Delhi we will meet you and transfer by to Shimla (343 kms / 8 hrs). Shimla is capital of himachal former capital of Britishers also set amidst, the snow copper, shaivalik,mountains which offer some of the most beautifull view of himalaya Reach there and check in hotel Dinner and overnight at Shimla.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Day 2: Shimla</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nMorning free. Afternoon half day city tour visiting Indian Institute Of Advanced Studies, Sankat Mochan Temple and Jakhu Temple, Evening free to stroll in the famous shopping place of Shimla town - The Mall &amp; The Ridge. Dinner and Overnight at hotel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Day 3 : Shimla - Manali</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAfter early breakfast you will proceed to Manali (320 kms/8 hrs) Manali is a perfect hill station covered with snow mountains and beautiful water falls. On arrival check in at hotel.- Dinner and overnight at Manali.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Day 4 : Manali</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nMorning after breakfast go for city tour visiting Hadimba Devi Temple, Manu Temple, Tibetan Monastery and Vashisht Village. Afternoon at leisure . Enjoy your dinner in hotel . Overnight at hotel.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Day 5 : Manali Rohtang Pass</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\null day excursion visiting Kothi Gorge, Gulaba, Marhi, Rohtang Pass -(tourist spot in himalaya having snow all 12 months) is the most visited tourist spot in Himalaya having snow round the year (Upto Snow Line in case Rohtang is closed due to snow fall) and Sollang Valley evening return to hotel . Diner and Overnight at hotel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Day 6 : Manali - Delhi (Departure)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAfter breakfast depart mananli and drive to Delhi 570 K M (11 hrs).<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'MANALI', ''),
